org.vadere.util.geometry.shapes

Class VRing

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vadere.util.geometry.shapes.VRing
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.Shape, VShape

    public class VRing
extends java.lang.Object
implements VShape
    A ring consists of two circles of different size. This shape can be used to simulate the experiment described in paper jelic-2012 and jelic-2012b.
